emails.body:

 Just letting you know my planned schedule for today.
  I am currently in the lab until 10:40.  Then after lecture I will be in the lab until 1pm.
  From 1 to 3 I will be in my ECE office and you can come there for questions and then back in the lab from 3:15 until 4:30
   Dan

emails.body:
Parliamentarians work to ensure fair, consistent senate proceedings.
 Bringing order to the 250-member Urbana-Champaign Senate is not a task for the fainthearted.

emails.subject: Why Amazon won't become the Amazon of Music
emails.body:
The company was founded in 1994,
 spurred by what Bezos called his regret minimization framework, which described his efforts to fend off any regrets for not participating sooner in the Internet business boom during that time.
  In 1994, Bezos left his employment as vice-president of D. E. Shaw & Co., a Wall Street firm, and moved to Seattle.
 He began to work on a business plan for what would eventually become Amazon.com.
